                    <p class="justin">First, you need to configure your device to allow for installation of apps outside of Google Play. <a href="http://go.blokada.org/info_sideload">Click here for a short video tutorial</a>. Then, simply click the button below:</p>
                    <br/><br/>
                    <p><a href="https://github.com/blokadaorg/blokada/releases/download/3.1.1/blokada-v3.1.1.apk" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-download"></i>  Download Blokada v3</a></p>
                    <br/>
                    <p><a href="https://bitbucket.org/blokada/blokada/downloads/blokada-origin-v2.2.3.apk"><i class="fa fa-download"></i>  Download Blokada v2 (Android 4+)</a></p>
                    <br/><br/>
                    <p class="justin" style="color:#777;">Note: Blokada isn't allowed on Google Play because it interferes with Google's business model. Please contact us in case you experience any problems. If for some reason you don't want to use the recommended way, Blokada is available on app stores listed below. Pick the one that suits you the most!</p>

                    <p><a href="https://f-droid.org/packages/org.blokada.alarm/"><img alt="Download Blokada ad blocker at F-Droid" src="https://fdroid.gitlab.io/artwork/badge/get-it-on.png" width="200" /></a></p>
