                <h2>Blokada is made by you</h2>
                <p class="justin">Blokada is an open source project, which means you can be sure <b>it's always going to be free, safe to use, and without any hidden agenda</b>. We believe this is the only right way to develop an ad blocker you can trust.</p>
                <p class="justin">However, developing a quality app like Blokada requires a considerable amount of resources. This project exists thanks to the support of <b>awesome people like you</b>!</p>

                <p><a class="dbox-donation-button" href="http://go.blokada.org/donate_donorbox" style="background:#DF5401 url(https://d1iczxrky3cnb2.cloudfront.net/white_logo.png) no-repeat 18px center; color: #fff;text-decoration: none;font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;display: inline-block;font-size: 16px;padding: 13px 17px 13px 56px; -webkit-border-radius: 2px; -moz-border-radius: 2px; border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 #9c3a00; text-shadow: 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);" >Donate</a></p>

